 blir tatt vare p\u00e5, og enten levert direkte tilbake til eieren, eller til politiets hittegodskontor, sier han.", "Det har ikke lyktes BT \u00e5 komme i kontakt med Norgestaxi."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "5bb1b9cb99a415c1bb1140e84630bde9ff2a4f7600e87557a83d73e25969ff87"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-28T22:59:16.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I juni glemte Adrian Rendell (20) mobiltelefonen sin igjen i en drosje. Onsdag ga den signaler fra seg i byen Arbil i Kurdistan."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10028661.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/adrianrendell.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/329381c54c0845627b375ed775d591ff66c6cbc7.jpg?58b600c4"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Adrians mobil dukket opp i Irak -adressa.no", "Fulgte telefonen via app", "Anmeldte saken", "Anbefaler sporing", "Kj\u00f8pte ny telefon", "Kvittering heretter"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "329381c54c0845627b375ed775d591ff66c6cbc7"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["telenor", "gjensidige"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["spore", "mobil dukket", "telefon"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["s\u00e6dalen", "iphonen", "norgestaxi", "find", "android", "kurdistan", "per arild meling", "bergenfest", "iphone"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["arbil", "irak"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["arne voll", "a